## Attribution

This software uses the following open source packages:

- React and React DOM for the user interface framework
- Material-UI for the component library and design system
- Electron for cross-platform desktop application capabilities
- TypeScript for type-safe JavaScript development
- Zustand for state management
- SQLite for local database storage
- Chokidar for file system monitoring
- Axios for HTTP client functionality
- Framer Motion for animations and transitions
- Jest for testing framework
- ESLint and Prettier for code quality
- Webpack and Babel for build tooling

We are grateful to all the open source contributors who made these projects possible.

